<plot>Nick, a hedonistic young man goes to Bali to surf. When he has an accident he is healed by a beautiful woman - a shaman with real magical powers. He falls in love with her but she's an outcast, like Nick's brother, with whom she develops a bond. He falls under her spell and has prophetic visions. Nick must enter the "unseen world" to save his brother from madness and Bali from a catastrophic natural disaster.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?057476</url></doc>
